e=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 26, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rxi1665702670406.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rxi1665702670406.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rxi1665702670406.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rxi1665702670406\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Packing Codes for Other Data\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__packing_codes_for_other_data_138436\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">String, Image, and Raw data can be mapped to a variety of packing codes, including <code class=\"ph codeph\">W</code> for Unicode characters.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__p_d44780e1_d44781e1_d44782e1\">Use the String data type for characters in any supported\n         character sets. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1665702670477.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1665702670477.html\" title=\"Meta character sets are used for translating installable character sets and defining translation tables. In earlier versions of Uniface, meta character sets were used as internal character sets instead of Unicode.\">Meta Character Sets</a>. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__p_d44783e1_d44784e1_d44785e1\">Use the Raw data type for fields containing raw data that should not be converted or processed. For example, raw is the data type to use for pictures and sound.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__p_d44786e1_d44787e1_d44788e1\">Use the Image data type for fields that contain images from the database, glyphs, disk files, or third-party filters.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__p_d44789e1_d44790e1_d44791e1\">If the underlying DBMS does not support the storage format determined by the packing code, the DBMS connector maps the information to the most suitable alternative. For more information, see the relevant connector documentation for your DBMS.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4337e1_d4338e1_d4339e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4337e1_d4338e1_d4339e1__entry__1\">\n Uniface Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4337e1_d4338e1_d4339e1__entry__2\">\n Default Packing Code\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4337e1_d4338e1_d4339e1__entry__1\">\n Image\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4337e1_d4338e1_d4339e1__entry__2\">\n R\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4337e1_d4338e1_d4339e1__entry__1\">\n Raw\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4337e1_d4338e1_d4339e1__entry__2\">\n R\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4337e1_d4338e1_d4339e1__entry__1\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4337e1_d4338e1_d4339e1__entry__2\">\n C40\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"5\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">String, Raw, and Variable Packing Codes</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__1\"></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__2\"></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__3\">\n Uniface Data Types\n </th>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__4\">\n Uniface Packing Code\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__5\">\n Explanation\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__6\">\n String\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__7\">\n Raw\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__8\">\n Image\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__1 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__4\">\n C (C40), C1-C*\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__2 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__5\">\n Character string\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__3 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__6\">\n Y\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__3 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__7\">\n Y\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__3 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__8\">\n Y\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__1 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__4\">\n R (R40), R1-R*\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__2 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__5\">\n Binary (raw)\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__3 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__6\">\n Y\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__3 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__7\">\n Y\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__3 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__8\">\n Y\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__1 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__4\">\n S (S40), S1-S*\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__2 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__5\">\n Character string\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__3 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__6\">\n Y\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__3 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__7\">\n Y\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__3 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__8\">\n Y\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__1 rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__4\">\n SC (SC40),SC1 SC*\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rxi1665702670406__table_d4340e1_d4341e1_d4342e1__entry__2 rx